{"id":147271,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shiver_(Coldplay_song)","text":"=\"preserve\">\"Shiver\" is a single released by rock band Coldplay. \"Shiver\" was released off the album \"Parachutes\" in March 2000. A re-release was released a year later in February 2001.\nFormat.\nThe format of the single by Coldplay is a CD. It plays as an Extended Play (or EP).","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Rock_and_roll","surface_form":"rock","offset":45},{"uri":"Coldplay","surface_form":"Coldplay","offset":55},{"uri":"Parachutes_(album)","surface_form":"Parachutes","offset":102},{"uri":"March","surface_form":"March","offset":117},{"uri":"2000","surface_form":"2000","offset":123},{"uri":"February","surface_form":"February","offset":171},{"uri":"2001","surface_form":"2001","offset":180},{"uri":"Coldplay","surface_form":"Coldplay","offset":222},{"uri":"Compact_disc","surface_form":"CD","offset":236},{"uri":"Extended_Play","surface_form":"Extended Play","offset":255}]}